{"tid":1802692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請問咩叫兄弟爬山，各自努力？","createTime":"2019-12-29T16:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T16:26:55.000Z","uid":143774,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e6ef7c2d0629c228e9533bf02e9e5fbd34c50a1f","tid":1802692,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T16:15:12.000Z","msg":"不篤灰<br />\n不割蓆<br />\n不分化呢？<br />\n<br />\n為咗一個獨立口號使唔使咁大火氣？<br />\n仲記唔記得當初嘅兄弟爬山？<br />\n<br />\n如果嘈交，請回憶起呢幾句，佢支持我哋行到而家，跌跌撞撞走咗半年多<br />\n<br />\n仲有捉鬼真係無意思，自己就係大台，值得去做就做，唔值就唔好去做，自己有智慧<br />\n<br />\n最後請相信前線，對家進步同時，大家都進緊步<br />\n由初初陣地到be water 再到快閃，每一樣都學習緊<br />\n<br />\n最後打氣，1月1見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老土講句，堅持總會勝利，2020 煲底相擁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RNF85UA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRNF85UA.png&h=b7f21992&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ff380ed8f115085655ad1b3e5b830295aa803e6","tid":1802692,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T16:19:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=98702b04\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e388833a934b2af6ff65301a0c8436f7a636fadb","tid":1802692,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T16:20:54.000Z","msg":"係港獨好大火氣，狂屌唔港獨嘅手足。"},{"pid":"7bc6c916fa9b6e85480a6473eb7005981598cc83","tid":1802692,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T16:26:55.000Z","msg":"邊個同佢地係兄弟